rows.label: qev041310_MSG0001
rows.name:
I once loved hunting. Thought nothing was better in life.
But collecting Miralife Cards is greater fun![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041310_MSG0002
rows.name:
Someday I will have full collection.
But only if I hide them from my wife.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041310_MSG0003
rows.name:
I love Miralife Cards. But I got carried away.
Neglected my wife. She got angry.
Took cards from me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041310_MSG0004
rows.name:
It is probably for best. But I still want silver evello card.
Do you have one?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041310_MSG0005
rows.name:
I have no cards to trade.
But I can offer secret hunting knowledge of Prone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041310_MSG0009
rows.name: I have longed for this card. Thank you, Earth alien.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041310_MSG0010
rows.name: Now I teach you ancient Prone hunting prowess.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041310_MSG0012
rows.name:
You are swift learner, Earth alien!
I name you honorary Prone hunter.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041310_MSG0013
rows.name:
I see. That is fine. I will find it on my own.
I will use wits and skill. This is Prone way![ST:wait ]
